Opera has a button in the UI -- Fast Forward -- that uses &lt;link rel=next&gt;.<br /><br />HTML5 does not mandate any particular UI. You should complain to the browser vendors directly about UI issues.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forums.whatwg.org/bb3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=4">zcorpan</a> — Mon Jul 20, 2009 7:51 pm</p><hr />
